`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The `pointerEvents="box-none"` on the overlay container (rather than `"none"`) is important: `"none"` would block all touch events (including the Skip button press), while `"box-none"` passes through touches that hit the container itself but lets child views (like `Pressable`) still receive input. This is the correct pattern for transparent overlay containers that host interactive children.
